<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV81">
<l>kaṭaintapāṟka ṭalkiṭantu kālanēmi yaikkaṭin</l>
<l>tuṭaintavāli taṉpiṉukku tavavanti rāmaṉāy</l>
<l>miṭaintavēḻma raṅkaḷuma ṭaṅkaveytuvēṅkaṭa</l>
<l>maṭaintamāla pātamē yaṭaintunāḷu muymmiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Won’t you be saved by always seeking the feet of Māl, who</l>
<l>—reclining on the milk ocean that was churned, destroying Kālanemi,</l>
<l>as Rāma, coming to help Vālin’s dispirited younger brother,</l>
<l>discharging arrows [through] all seven trees that were closely set—</l>
<l rend="indent">Reached Vēṅkaṭam?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
